default3. Extending regulation to other professional and occupatdefaultional groupsdefault3.1
default              
defaultWe have a track record of extending regulation to 
defaultfurther 
defaultprofessions. Since 
defaultour Register opened in 2003
default, we have registe
defaultred four additional professions. Most recently 
