default 
defaultof fitness to practise allegations
default against registrants has shown t
defaulthat t
defaulthe majority
default of cases
default 
default(72% in 2012-13)
default 
defaultare about conduct
default and professionalism
default with relatively few cases purely about lack of competence. 
defaultWe have been undertaking a programme of work and research to build 
defaultthe 
defaultevidence base 
defaultfurther 
defaultand inform decisions ab
defaultout how we approach the assessment 
defaultof continuing fitness to practis
defaulte. 
